title: US, Europe Futures Edge Up Before Rate Decisions: Markets Wrap
summary: US and European equity futures climbed while Asian stocks were mixed as investors awaited interest rate decisions this week from the US, Europe, China and Japan. A gauge of dollar strength was steady and Treasury yields were marginally higher.
